    <p>Com­pa­nies of all sizes will re­ceive more sup­port in se­cur­ing green and sus­tain­abil­ity-linked loans with a new grant scheme launched by the Mon­e­tary Author­ity of Sin­ga­pore (MAS) yes­ter­day. The Green and Sus­tain­abil­ity-Linked Loan Grant Scheme is a world first and will start next Jan­uary, said MAS.</p>


